description: PRICE REDUCTION! Urban living in the heart of Seattle! This tastefully updated 10th-floor corner condo in First Hill offers stunning natural light, open layout, and a spacious private deck. Enjoy year-round comfort with A/C in living area, radiant heat, and a cozy gas fireplace, adding both warmth and ambience. Full size washer and dryer in unit.  Furnishings may be included with an acceptable offer-just bring your suitcase! Blocks from the Puget Sound and a short 18-minute walk from Pike Place Market! Amenities include community lounge, large shared deck, and fitness room. Walkability Score 99/Transit 100--city life couldn't be more convenient! Pre-inspected! Ask listing agent about lender incentive of $2K toward closing costs!
